overview: NWA Crockett Cup 2022 is the first PPV event of the National Wrestling Alliance for the year 2022. Along with other matches, the event will feature matches of the 5th Jim Crockett Sr. Memorial Crocket Cup Tag Team Tournament. Wrestling Legend Jeff Jerrett is the ambassador for the tournament.  The event will take place over two nights on March 19 and March 20 from Tennessee State Fairground Sports Arena in Nashville, TN.
title: NWA Crockett Cup 2022: Night 1
